|---|---|---|---|
| **activity-init** | `skills/activity-init/` | Establish product context and technical guidelines | `product-engineer` |
| **activity-refine** | `skills/activity-refine/` | Clarify scope â€” issue refinement or full PRD creation | `product-engineer` |
