## Workflow Chains

### Full Feature (PRD-Driven)

```
product-engineer: refine â†’ generate-spec â†’ generate-stories â†’ publish-github â†’ plan
                                                                                  â†“
developer: implement
```

### Single GitHub Issue

```
product-engineer: refine â†’ plan
                            â†“
developer: implement
```

### Multi-Story Orchestration

```
product-engineer: refine â†’ generate-spec â†’ generate-stories â†’ publish-github â†’ plan
                                                                                  â†“
planner: orchestrate â†’ developer: implement (per story, sequential)
```

### Quick Fix (Clear Issue, Task List Exists)

```
developer: implement
```

### UX Validation Loop

```
product-engineer: refine â†’ generate-spec
                               â†“
ux-engineer: mockups â†’ gap analysis â†’ refinement handoff
                                          â†“
product-engineer: update spec/stories
```

### Test-First Design (Verifier)

```
product-engineer: refine â†’ spec â†’ stories â†’ plan
                                                 â†“
verifier (design mode): generate test plan (from spec or stories)
                                                 â†“
developer: implement (feature + tests from test plan)
                                                 â†“
verifier (audit mode): grey-box fidelity audit â†’ fidelity report
```

### Project Initialization

```
product-engineer (init mode): activity-init â†’ product-context.md + technical-guidelines.md
```

